e Time' Characters|url=http://screencrush.com/adventure-time-voice-cast/|publisher=ScreenCrush|accessdate=2017-03-27|date=2013-07-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140527213242/http://screencrush.com/adventure-time-voice-cast/|archive-date=2014-05-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>配音時，劇組成員會聚在一起共同完成錄音，而非像其他動畫一樣每人單獨錄制自己的台詞再剪輯到一起。沃爾什曾表示劇集的錄音過程「類似劇本圍讀」。這種錄音方式使得人物對白更加自然，其效果也獲得好評。<ref>{{cite AV media|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lo8ItRHrEHk|title=Adventure Time – Season 3 Comic-Con Exclusive: Hynden Walch|publisher=YouTube|date=2011-08-08|accessdate=2017-03-19|time=02:35|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140201003219/http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lo8ItRHrEHk|archive-date=2014-02-01|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="people">{{cite web|last1=Heigl|first1=Alex|title=Emmys 2016: Adventure Time and Its Path to Success|url=http://people.com/awards/emmys-2016-adventure-time-and-its-path-to-success/|publisher=People|accessdate=2017-03-19|date=2016-09-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161112095804/http://people.com/awards/emmys-2016-adventure-time-and-its-path-to-success/|archive-date=2016-11-12|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=ADVENTURE TIME Headed to the Big Screen?|url=http://www.broadwayworld.com/bwwtv/article/ADVENTURE-TIME-Headed-to-the-Big-Screen-20150228|publisher=Broadway World|accessdate=2017-03-19|date=2015-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150717234528/http://www.broadwayworld.com/bwwtv/article/ADVENTURE-TIME-Headed-to-the-Big-Screen-20150228|archive-date=2015-07-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>

