==播出和反响==

===收视===
第二季於2010年10月11日首播。首集〈[[惡夜魔境|惡夜魔境]]〉播出後獲得200.1萬觀眾的收視，<ref name=nightratings/>比上一季首播集略低，但高於上一季季終集。<ref name=firstep>{{cite web|url=http://tvbythenumbers.com/2010/04/06/monday-cable-pawning-damages-em-nurse-jackie-damaged/47625 |title=Monday Cable: Pawning & Picking Good for History; "Damages " & "Nurse Jackie" Damaged |first=Robert |last=Seidman |date=2010-04-06 |accessdate=2017-03-27 |work=[[TV_by_the_Numbers|TV by the Numbers]] |publisher=Zap2it |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100411035123/http://tvbythenumbers.com/2010/04/06/monday-cable-pawning-damages-em-nurse-jackie-damaged/47625 |archivedate=2010-04-11}}</ref><ref name=finale1>{{cite web|title=Monday's Cable Ratings: 'MNF' a Ratings Juggernaut|url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/ratings/2010/09/28/mondays-cable-ratings-mnf-a-ratings-juggernaut-37654/cable_20100927/|publisher=The Futon Critic|accessdate=2017-03-27|date=2010-09-28}}</ref>這一集比前一年同一檔期的收視率也有明顯提升，收視人數上漲超過30%。其中9-14歲年齡段觀眾上漲最多，漲幅達到59%。<ref>{{cite web|last=Gorman|first=Bill|title=Ratings Notes for TBS, TNT, Cartoon Network, Adult Swim and truTV; Including MLB Division Series Averages|url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2010/10/12/ratings-notes-for-tbs-tnt-cartoon-network-adult-swim-and-trutv-including-mlb-division-series-averages/67703/|work=[[TV_by_the_Numbers|TV by the Numbers]]|publisher=Zap2it|accessdate=2017-03-27|date=2010-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304205855/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2010/10/12/ratings-notes-for-tbs-tnt-cartoon-network-adult-swim-and-trutv-including-mlb-division-series-averages/67703/|archive-date=2016-03-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>第二季第3集〈效忠國王〉收穫了逾254.1萬觀眾，是該季中收視人數最高的一集。<ref name=loyalratings/> 

第二季原計劃在2011年5月2日連播〈[[愚笨的人類/人類大反擊|愚笨的人類]]〉和〈[[愚笨的人類/人類大反擊|愚笨的人類]]〉兩集收尾，為下一季留下懸念。但節目編排因故調整，原定在4月25日播出的第24集〈吸血鬼訓練課〉在當日臨時推遲至5月9日作為季終的第26集播出，〈愚笨的人類〉和〈人類大反擊〉兩集播出時間不變，因此成為第24和25集。<ref>{{cite web|title=Last Minute Programming Change |url=http://pwcartoons.frederator.com/post/4941767054 |publisher=Frederator Studios |accessdate=2017-03-22 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140905040749/http://pwcartoons.frederator.com/post/4941767054/last-minute-programming-change-remember-when-we |archivedate=2014-09-05 |date=2011-04-25 |quote=Remember when we said "Heat Signature", the episode where Marceline and pals convince Finn & Jake they're vampires, premieres tonight? That's a lie, actually. "Heat Signature" will air in two weeks, on May 9. It'll be the final new episode of season two. The big half-hour season finale, though, is still set for next Monday, May 2. In other words, Adventure Time is so special that its season finale airs before the season's final airing! In any event, sorry for the misinformation.— Eric |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ttdila.com/2011/05/beware-lich-king.html |title=Beware the Lich King |publisher=Thing To Do In LA |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110528031017/http://www.ttdila.com/2011/05/beware-lich-king.html |archivedate=2011-05-28 |accessdate=2017-03-22 |date=2011-05-02 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name="ign2"/>〈吸血鬼訓練課〉一集收視人數達到197.5萬，高於第一季季終集的收視數據。<ref name=heatsignature/><ref name=finale1/>

===評價和獲獎===
第二季播出後獲得評論界的廣泛贊譽，其中首集〈惡夜魔境〉尤其獲得好評。家庭娛樂網站{{lang|en|DVD Talk}}評論人泰勒·福斯特（{{lang|en|Tyler Foster}}）稱贊這一集「恰當地展示了」這部動畫包含的所有元素。福斯特認為這一集中艾薇爾和父親之間的矛盾以嚴肅正經的方式得到解決，同時整集中又充滿荒誕搞笑的情節，嚴肅和荒誕能完美結合，毫不突兀。他還認為這一集的歌曲也為劇集增添了色彩。<ref name=dvdtalk>{{cite web|last=Foster|first=Tyler|title=Adventure Time: It Came From the Nightosphere|url=http://www.dvdtalk.com/reviews/53920/adventure-time-it-came-from-the-nightosphere/|work=DVD Talk|publisher=Internet Brands|accessdate=2017-03-27|date=2012-03-06|archive-url=https://archive.today/20140802104833/http://www.dvdtalk.com/reviews/53920/adventure-time-it-came-from-the-nightosphere/|archive-date=2014-08-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>第二季播出後曾發行了一版DVD收錄了前兩季中的16集，其中包括〈惡夜魔境〉一集。[[MTV|MTV]]撰稿人查爾斯·韋伯（{{lang|en|Charles Webb}}）高度評價此集，認為其是這版DVD中的最大亮點。<ref>{{cite web|last=Webb|first=Charles|title=DVD Review: 'Adventure Time: It Came From the Nightosphere'|url=http://geek-news.mtv.com/2012/03/08/dvd-review-adventure-time-it-came-from-the-nightosphere/|work=MTV Geek|publisher=[[音樂電視網|MTV]]|accessdate=2017-03-27|date=2012-03-18|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120911010044/http://geek-news.mtv.com/2012/03/08/dvd-review-adventure-time-it-came-from-the-nightosphere/|archivedate=2012-09-11}}</ref>評論網站[[IGN|IGN]]的馬特·福勒（{{lang|en|Matt Fowler}}）更是稱這一集為「經典之作」，<ref name=ign1>{{cite web|last=Fowler |first=Matt |title=Adventure Time Creator: It's Awesome If We Give People Nightmares |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2012/03/05/adventure-time-creator-its-awesome-if-we-give-people-nightmares |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161204073610/http://www.ign.com/articles/2012/03/05/adventure-time-creator-its-awesome-if-we-give-people-nightmares |archivedate=2016-12-04 |work=[[IGN|IGN]] |publisher=[[新闻集团_(1979－2013年)|News Corporation]] |accessdate=2017-03-27 |date=2012-03-05 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>認為其代表了《探險活寶》的最高水準。<ref name="ign2"/>這一集之後被2011年美國電視業最高獎[[第63屆黃金時段艾美獎|第63屆黃金時段艾美獎]]「最佳短篇動畫節目」提名，但未能獲獎。<ref name="emmys.com">{{cite web|title=Outstanding Short-Form Animated Program 2011|url=http://www.emmys.com/awards/nominees-winners/2011/outstanding-short-format-animated-program|work=Emmys.com|publisher=Academy of Television Arts & Sciences|accessdate=2017-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170409001433/http://www.emmys.com/awards/nominees-winners/2011/outstanding-short-format-animated-program|archive-date=2017-04-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>

第二季整季亦獲得正面評價。影評網站[[IndieWire|IndieWire]]編輯格雷格·埃爾巴爾（{{lang|en|Greg Ehrbar}}）認為其完美地命中目標人群「兒童和青少年」，同時又「毋庸置疑」適合成年人觀看，稱其中角色「比很多[[黃金時段|黃金時段]]節目中的人物更有深度」，在幽默之余有很多「暖心」的細節。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.indiewire.com/2013/06/dvd-review-adventure-time-seasons-1-and-2-122873/|title=DVD REVIEW: “Adventure Time” Seasons 1 and 2|publisher=IndieWire|date=2013-06-14|accessdate=2017-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170403014407/http://www.indiewire.com/2013/06/dvd-review-adventure-time-seasons-1-and-2-122873/|archive-date=2017-04-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>馬特·福勒也高度評價這一季，盛贊其人物鮮活。他認為這一季在保留了第一季元素的同時又「成功地拓展開來」。他指出劇集自這一季開始略有黑暗，出現了前一季中沒有的反面角色和陰暗笑話，尤其是結尾的〈愚笨的人類〉和〈人類大反擊〉這兩集「強大有力」。<ref name="ign2">{{cite web|last=Fowler |first=Matt |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/06/27/adventure-time-the-complete-second-season-blu-ray-review |title=ADVENTURE TIME: THE COMPLETE SECOND SEASON BLU-RAY REVIEW |work=[[IGN|IGN]] |publisher=[[新聞集團_(1979－2013年)|News Corporation]] |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150925201511/http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/06/27/adventure-time-the-complete-second-season-blu-ray-review |archivedate=2015-09-25 |accessdate=2017-03-27 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>泰勒·福斯特在評論第二季DVD套裝時給本季內容打出五星滿分評價。他「極力推薦」這一季，認為其探索並拓展了第一季建立的世界觀，稱其「融合了各種元素」，「罕有作品能達到如此高度」。福斯特稱第二季中的場景、人物大多在第一季已經出現過，但仍然能始終保持新意。他戲稱劇組「詭計多端」，而第二季末為後續內容設下的伏筆更是俘獲觀眾的「一大利器」。<ref name=dvdtalk2/>但福斯特對DVD中的視頻質量略有不滿，指出DVD的色彩雖然完美，但偶有[[混疊|疊影]]出現。他對DVD的附加內容也不甚滿意，稱沃德親自錄制的評論音軌雖然是一大特色之處，但剪輯不盡如人意。<ref name=dvdtalk2>{{cite web|last=Foster|first=Tyler|title=Adventure Time: The Complete Second Season (Blu-ray)|url=http://www.dvdtalk.com/reviews/60149/cartoon-network-adventure-time-complete-2nd-season/|work=DVD Talk|publisher=Internet Brands|accessdate=2017-03-27|date=2013-06-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303222947/http://www.dvdtalk.com/reviews/60149/cartoon-network-adventure-time-complete-2nd-season/|archive-date=2016-03-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>

